{"tid":935378,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BL路飛比卡超　大英博物館辦日本漫畫展 規模係國外展覽史上最大","createTime":"2018-12-10T03:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T03:44:31.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b7a2c9e749cc9b403955c9eb58d05923c3e867","tid":935378,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/1293_0VqT1_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F1293_0VqT1_1200x0.jpg&h=28548420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《波族傳奇》<br />\n<br />\n大英博物館將於明年 5 月 23 日至 8 月 26 日舉行大型日本漫畫展「Manga マンガ」，是為世界史上最大規模的日本國外漫畫展覽。<br />\n<br />\n展覽內容相當廣泛。當中包括漫畫史，如浮世繪畫家葛飾北齋（1760～1849 年）的作品、河鍋曉齋於 1880 年繪畫的《新富座妖怪引幕》等。此外亦有漫畫的衍生文化產物，如動畫、遊戲、Cosplay 和同人誌。一些新興玩意如 Pok&eacute;mon Go 也是展覽介紹對象之一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/theatre-curtain-approved_g5PKi_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftheatre-curtain-approved_g5PKi_1200x0.jpg&h=d3bdffd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《新富座妖怪引幕》<br />\n<br />\n不過當中最重要的，當然仍是漫畫本身。策展人 Nicole Rousmaniere 表示，展覽將展示不同類型的作品，包括 BL （Boy's Love）名作如《波族傳奇》、《風與木之詩》等。Nicole 直言不會迴避性與暴力之類的「成人」議題。她解釋何謂 BL 時這樣說﹕「基本上是年輕男子之間的愛情表現，有趣的是大多作品都是由女人繪畫，而讀者也是女人為主。」她又指，「很多人覺得某程度上對女人、特別是年輕女人來說，幻想『關於男人的事』比較安全。這令她們不那麼尷尬，也可以讓她們抽離於自己面對的現實。」<br />\n<br />\n已知將會登場的作品有《聖哥傳》、《寵物小精靈》、《小飛俠阿童木》、《ONE PIECE》、《龍珠》等，當中部份作品如《聖哥傳》的原畫，更已成為大英博物館的藏品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/bpanews_3d5ad788-c5e9-4e7f-98a5-3e13e0cd9f52_embedded240054695_x70kO_1200x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fbpanews_3d5ad788-c5e9-4e7f-98a5-3e13e0cd9f52_embedded240054695_x70kO_1200x0.jpeg&h=856715a9&s={SIZE}\" />《黃金神威》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/2461_r1Vm0_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F2461_r1Vm0_1200x0.jpg&h=012eb0c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n展品之一的《甜甜私房貓》<br />\n <br />\n大英博物館館長 Hartwig Fischer 於記者會上如此說﹕「堅信從全世界訪問大英博物館的人都將享受這次展覽會。」平時記者當這些是公關修辭，但今次，睇怕都應該算合理推測﹗<br />\n<br />\n相關報道<br />\n<br />\nFT、獨立報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%94%94%E8%A8%88%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-%E9%8A%80%E6%B2%B3%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7-bl%E8%B7%AF%E9%A3%9B%E6%AF%94%E5%8D%A1%E8%B6%85-%E5%A4%A7%E8%8B%B1%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8%E8%BE%A6%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%B1%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25A8%2588%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC-%25E9%258A%2580%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7-bl%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%25A3%259B%25E6%25AF%2594%25E5%258D%25A1%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25B1%2595%2F&d=VfU7UGqeyHdBUD1vc26TcYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=b577c2b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25A8%2588%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC-%25E9%258A%2580%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7-bl%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%25A3%259B%25E6%25AF%2594%25E5%258D%25A1%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25B1%2595%2F&h=b3413870\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%94%94%E8%A8%88%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-%E9%8A%80%E6%B2%B3%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7-bl%E8%B7%AF%E9%A3%9B%E6%AF%94%E5%8D%A1%E8%B6%85-%E5%A4%A7%E8%8B%B1%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8%E8%BE%A6%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%B1%95/</a>"},{"pid":"3bab33b529a6509ed452d1ba328b4c73192339b3","tid":935378,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:44:31.000Z","msg":"垃場竟然用寵物小精靈，比着毒果一早用左精靈寶可夢"}]